descriptionHtml:
[font=Courier New]Hi,this is my first mod for Skyrim,it's just a simple bodyslide preset that i thought some of ya'll would like :)

[/font]This is not supposed to be a realistic preset.

Install:drag and drop .xml file into Skyrim/Data/CalienteTools/Bodyslide/SliderPresets and build the CBBE meshes in Bodyslide :)

Requirements:
Caliente's Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE- by [b]Caliente_ Ousnius and Jeir[/b] :http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?
BodySlide and Outfit Studio by [b]Ousnius and Caliente[/b] :http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015/?
author: BR1
